{"title":"使用 hexo 生成 Post","date":"2019-01-31T16:00:00.000Z","thumbnail":"imgs/01.jpg","slug":"hexo-generate-post","tags":["Course","Experience","Hexo"],"categories":["Web-Log"],"updated":"2019-05-12T13:59:39.072Z","content":"<h2 id=\"环境\">环境<a href=\"post/hexo-generate-post#环境\"></a></h2><p>下文 “.\\” 指的是hexo根目录,所有的命令在终端执行</p>\n<p> (1) 安装Git</p>\n<p>下载地址：<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/downloads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://git-scm.com/downloads</a></p>\n<p> (2) 安装NodeJS</p>\n<p>下载地址：<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/download/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://nodejs.org/download/</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"配置git\">配置git<a href=\"post/hexo-generate-post#配置git\"></a></h2><p> (1) 设置你的Git name</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.name <span class=\"string\">\"usename\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.email <span class=\"string\">\"email\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p> (2) 生成SSH秘钥</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class=\"string\">\"you email\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>连续回车即可</p>\n<p>可以在主目录下的 “.ssh” 文件夹下得到两个文件:<code>id_rsa</code> 和 <code>id_rsa.pub</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"配置-GitHub\">配置 GitHub<a href=\"post/hexo-generate-post#配置-GitHub\"></a></h2><p> (1) 注册 github</p>\n<p>地址: <a href=\"https://github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://github.com/</a></p>\n<p>按照提示注册就可以,邮箱一定要真实(要验证邮箱),否则无法创建存储库</p>\n<p> (2) 创建github存储库</p>\n<p>仓库的名字要和你的账号对应，如 “name.github.io” (“name” 是你的用户名)</p>\n<p>然后选择Create repository</p>\n<p> (3) 把<code>id_rsa.pub</code>内容复制,添加到GitHub</p>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/02/01/5c53ac546c0af.png\" alt data-zoomable></p></div>\n<p>验证SSH是否生效</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>看到<code>Hi</code>后面是你的用户名，就说明成功了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装hexo\">安装hexo<a href=\"post/hexo-generate-post#安装hexo\"></a></h2><p> (1) 更改npm源为淘宝源提高速度</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> registry http://registry.npm.taobao.org/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p> (2) 安装 Hexo 并初始化</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>跳到一个合适的目录,初始化hexo</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>hexo 根目录,执行 <code>hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</code></p>\n<p>打开<a href=\"http://localhost:4000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://localhost:4000</a>(默认),你就可以看到你的博客的样子了</p>\n<p>你可以使用<kbd>Ctrl+C</kbd>来结束hexo sever</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>参考链接<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo官方文档</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"Depoy\">Depoy<a href=\"post/hexo-generate-post#Depoy\"></a></h3><p>(1) 修改的<code>.\\_config.yml</code>文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">deploy:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">- type:</span> <span class=\"string\">git</span>    <span class=\"comment\">#不需要更改</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">  repo:</span>        <span class=\"comment\">#存储库地址</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>(2) 使用<code>hexo depoy</code>部署到GitHub</p>\n<p>安装git部署服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后执行<code>hexo d</code>推送成功后就可以 让你的站点被其他人访问了</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Alan Wan</p>\n<p>Last change: May 12, 2019</p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world"},"link":"https://kaze.xyz/post/hexo-generate-post/","toc":[{"title":"环境","id":"环境","index":"1"},{"title":"配置git","id":"配置git","index":"2"},{"title":"配置 GitHub","id":"配置-GitHub","index":"3"},{"title":"安装hexo","id":"安装hexo","index":"4","children":[{"title":"Depoy","id":"Depoy","index":"4.1"}]}],"copyright":{"license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","author":"Alan Wan","link":"<a href=\"https://kaze.xyz/post/hexo-generate-post/\" title=\"使用 hexo 生成 Post\">https://kaze.xyz/post/hexo-generate-post/</a>"}}